column24: Give the gift of choice with an Amazon Gift Card, redeemable towards millions of items on Amazon or find their registry and give a gift they'll love. Just open the menu, go to See All Programs and tap Gift Cards & Registry.
• Improvements for reliability and speed
• Organize your memos, links, photos, and more in Keep with the new collection feature.

Thanks for using Google Maps! This release brings bug fixes that improve our product to help you discover new places and navigate to them.

Become a beta tester: http://goo.gl/vLUcaJ

column1: Messenger – Text and Video Chat for Free
column24:
The brand new, redesigned Messenger app is now easier to use, simpler to navigate and more fun.

Messenger has been simplified into three tabs—People, Chat and Discover.

-Chat tab lets you quickly access all your messages.

-People tab helps you find friends, both new and old.

-Discover tab connects you to your favorite brands, find discounts, play games and more in explore.

Plus, new color gradients make your chat more colorful too!

See the big picture in Outlook by adding calendars that are already syncing to your phone. Now you can access all of your events from one convenient location. All of our weekly updates also include performance improvements and bug fixes to make Outlook better for you.
You worry about what to watch next, we’re busy making that experience even better.
* New Charms! Tap the avatar for one of your Groups to see who’s taken the most screenshots, shared the most memories, sent the most Bitmojis and more.

What's New in v7.0.4:
- Music Search Added for Time Capsules.
- Registration adds Facebook Login option.
- Moments Privacy Settings: Last 1 month viewable by friends.

• Security fix for CVE-2019-3568.
• Consecutive Voice Messages will now play in sequence, so you don't have to press play on each message.

v8.20.8059-1.N
* Bug fixes
